{"tid":1658403,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"只有香港人救到香港 講撚完","createTime":"2019-10-16T13:13:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-16T14:05:14.000Z","uid":113222,"like":26,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"3f4c0c956a2c4753d7f8d2efab5b2133ee7cc5d5","tid":1658403,"uid":113222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T13:13:23.000Z","msg":"咪撚再乜都顧住美國，無任何國家會無利益就走黎幫你。就算人權法案過左，實際上點實行，都係行政機關決定，即係特朗普話事，佢為左同中共deal，必要時一腳踢撚開香港。<br />\n<br />\n唔係話完全唔打國際牌，但無可能淨係靠打國際牌，而家岑子杰差d命都無，你班仆街淨係顧美國點睇？<br />\n<br />\n肯醒未？仲望住個天等人打救？香港之所以行到呢步都只係靠自己，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">只有香港人可以救到香港</span></span>。仲係呢種等人救嘅心態，輸撚硬。"},{"pid":"7aae6f4a60497f7012bfb1ef1bd5b0ccf400ef93","tid":1658403,"uid":17698,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T13:14:20.000Z","msg":"香港人反抗！"},{"pid":"37faa799e6fdcfd1a36226ec0e47bc0c5c7edfcc","tid":1658403,"uid":1834,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T13:14:42.000Z","msg":"同G20前一樣<br />\n成日諗住坐係冷氣房個民主會自己趺落黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6516dd23a767270348ae9510166f4bb7fdccfdce","tid":1658403,"uid":113222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"37faa799e6fdcfd1a36226ec0e47bc0c5c7edfcc","tid":1658403,"uid":1834,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T13:14:42.000Z","msg":"同G20前一樣<br />\n成日諗住坐係冷氣房個民主會自己趺落黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T13:15:00.000Z","msg":"反駁唔到"},{"pid":"a523d5c110446974eaba206e7a34e26b3d8c5012","tid":1658403,"uid":95588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T13:17:32.000Z","msg":"香港人反抗！"},{"pid":"2f32bd3ee19b944f5849931bdb0376af1b4b444d","tid":1658403,"uid":113222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T13:24:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fcb8905341620dc4b32a7ba2eccfa8457000458b","tid":1658403,"uid":214502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"q